data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom single-family home located in the sought-after Knights Bridge subdivision of Conyers. With a generous 3,838 square feet, this enchanting residence offers an open floorplan that seamlessly combines style and functionality. As you enter through the impressive 2-story foyer, you'll be captivated by the spacious family room featuring a cozy stone fireplace. Indulge in the oversized master suite with a separate sitting room and a charming fireplace. The large kitchen boasts a huge island perfect for culinary adventures. Tray ceilings, hardwood floors, and exterior lighting add to the allure of this great property. With a 3-car garage, a keeping room, and a great location, this home truly has it all. Motivated seller.
